s="nav" id="VPSidebarNav" aria-labelledby="sidebar-aria-label" tabindex="-1" data-v-319d5ca6><span class="visually-hidden" id="sidebar-aria-label" data-v-319d5ca6> Sidebar Navigation </span><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><div class="no-transition group" data-v-c40bc020><section class="VPSidebarItem level-0 has-active" data-v-c40bc020 data-v-b3fd67f8><!----><div class="items" data-v-b3fd67f8><!--[--><div class="VPSidebarItem level-1 is-link" data-v-b3fd67f8 data-v-b3fd67f8><div class="item" data-v-b3fd67f8><div class="indicator" data-v-b3fd67f8></div><a class="VPLink link link" href="/introduction/what-is-star-atlas" data-v-b3fd67f8><!--[--><p class="text" data-v-b3fd67f8>What is Star Atlas?</p><!--]--></a><!----></div><!----></div><div class="VPSidebarItem level-1 is-link" data-v-b3fd67f8 data-v-b3fd67f8><div class="item" data-v-b3fd67f8><div class="indicator" data-v-b3fd67f8></div><a class="VPLink link link" href="/introduction/what-is-build" data-v-b3fd67f8><!--[--><p class="text" data-v-b3fd67f8>What is Build?</p><!--]--></a><!----></div><!----></div><div class="VPSidebarItem level-1 is-link" data-v-b3fd67f8 data-v-b3fd67f8><div class="item" data-v-b3fd67f8><div class="indicator" data-v-b3fd67f8></div><a class="VPLink link link" href="/introduction/what-you-can-build" data-v-b3fd67f8><!--[--><p class="text" data-v-b3fd67f8>What You Can Build</p><!--]--></a><!----></div><!----></div><!--]--></div></section></div><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--></nav></aside><div class="VPContent has-sidebar" id="VPContent" data-v-5d98c3a5 data-v-1428d186><div class="VPDoc has-sidebar has-aside" data-v-1428d186 data-v-39a288b8><!--[--><!--]--><div class="container" data-v-39a288b8><div class="aside" data-v-39a288b8><div class="aside-curtain" data-v-39a288b8></div><div class="aside-container" data-v-39a288b8><div class="aside-content" data-v-39a288b8><div class="VPDocAside" data-v-39a288b8 data-v-3f215769><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--><nav aria-labelledby="doc-outline-aria-label" class="VPDocAsideOutline" data-v-3f215769 data-v-a5bbad30><div class="content" data-v-a5bbad30><div class="outline-marker" data-v-a5bbad30></div><div aria-level="2" class="outline-title" id="doc-outline-aria-label" role="heading" data-v-a5bbad30>On this page</div><ul class="VPDocOutlineItem root" data-v-a5bbad30 data-v-b933a997><!--[--><!--]--></ul></div></nav><!--[--><!--]--><div class="spacer" data-v-3f215769></div><!--[--><!--]--><!----><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--></div></div></div></div><div class="content" data-v-39a288b8><div class="content-container" data-v-39a288b8><!--[--><!--]--><main class="main" data-v-39a288b8><div style="position:relative;" class="vp-doc _introduction_what-you-can-build" data-v-39a288b8><div><h1 id="what-you-can-build" tabindex="-1">What You Can Build <a class="header-anchor" href="#what-you-can-build" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;What You Can Build&quot;">​</a></h1><p>Tools, games, guides, merch, dashboards, it’s all happening here.<br> The Star Atlas community has already launched dozens of impressive projects. From on-chain automation tools to merch stores, here’s just a glimpse of what people are building and what you can create too.</p><h4 id="gameplay-tools-automation" tabindex="-1">Gameplay Tools &amp; Automation <a class="header-anchor" href="#gameplay-tools-automation" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Gameplay Tools &amp; Automation&quot;">​</a></h4><ul><li><a href="https://atlas.eveeye.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">EVE Eye Map Tools</a></li><li><a href="https://medium.com/@atom_tool/atom-play-star-atlas-sage-without-limits-e6bc35282cf2" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">ATOM Automation Tool</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/Swift42/SLY-Assistant" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">SLY Assistant (GitHub)</a></li><li><a href="https://sa-dispatcher.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">SA Dispatcher</a></li></ul><h4 id="dashboards-data" tabindex="-1">Dashboards &amp; Data <a class="header-anchor" href="#dashboards-data" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Dashboards &amp; Data&quot;">​</a></h4><ul><li><a href="https://aephia.com/star-atlas-ships/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Aephia Ships &amp; Tools</a></li><li><a href="https://flipsidecrypto.xyz/Aephia/star-atlas---global-overview-NOleL4" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Global Overview (Flipside)</a></li><li><a href="https://flipsidecrypto.xyz/steven-sabol-dir-of-economy/star-atlas-dac-statistics-Nqbhc1?tabIndex=5" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">DAC Stats – Steven Sabol</a></li><li><a href="https://explorer.staratlas.club/factions/asset-charts" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Star Atlas Explorer – The Club</a></li><li><a href="https://redspatula.io/star-atlas-ships/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">RedSpatula Tools</a></li><li><a href="https://heimdall-industries.org/ship-markets/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Heimdall Ship Markets</a></li><li><a href="https://stardusteconomy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Stardust Economy</a></li><li><a href="https://galacticdash.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Galactic Dash</a></li><li><a href="https://data.guildcoexist.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Coexist Data Hub</a></li><li><a href="https://app.staratlasitalia.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Italia Dashboard</a></li><li><a href="https://bit.ly/access-star-atlas-nft-markets" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">NFT Market Data Sheet</a></li></ul><p>Escrow &amp; Markets</p><ul><li><a href="https://escrow.skullnbones.xyz/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">S&amp;B Escrow Service</a></li><li><a href="https://market.skullnbones.xyz/#/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">S&amp;B Market</a></li></ul><p>Guides &amp; Help</p><ul><li><a href="https://staratlas.help/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">staratlas.help</a></li><li><a href="https://staratlasguide.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">staratlasguide.com</a></li><li><a href="https://staratlasitalia.com/rubriche/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Italia Guides</a></li><li><a href="https://aephia.com/star-atlas-guides/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Aephia Guides</a></li><li><a href="https://intergalacticherald.com/star-atlas-guide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Intergalactic Herald Guides</a></li><li><a href="https://galiacrafters.medium.com/star-atlas-101-i-have-20-what-can-i-do-3e9c72e421d2" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GaliaCrafters SA 101</a></li><li><a href="https://hologramnews.com/star-atlas-guides/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">The Hologram Guides</a></li><li><a href="https://www.vnonymus-star.com/academia" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Vnonymus-Star Academia (ES)</a></li><li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DJTNQ5x-loI" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">SAGE for Small Players – YouTube</a></li></ul><p>Games</p><ul><li><a href="https://gx.games/games/h5jctu/star-atlas-tufa-attack/tracks/557a4223-d9d5-4976-8bc0-ad85b31bd800/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Tufa Attack – Arcade Game</a></li><li><a href="https://discord.gg/valleyarcade" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Valley Arcade – Discord</a></li></ul><p>Guild Resources</p><ul><li><a href="https://intergalacticherald.com/guilds/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">DAC Explorer – Intergalactic Herald</a></li><li><a href="https://atless.io/research/guilds/guild-list.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Guild List – Atlessio</a></li><li><a href="https://deepprofits.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">DeepProfits</a></li></ul><p>Merch, Art &amp; Fun</p><ul><li><a href="https://galiamerchants.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Galia Merchants</a></li><li><a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/StarArtisanShop" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Star Artisan Etsy Shop</a></li><li><a href="https://darkcoreroasters.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Dark Core Roasters</a></li><li><a href="https://www.galiaartstation.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Galia Art Station – 3D Ships</a></li><li><a href="https://suit-up.staratlas.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Profile Picture Generator</a></li><li><a href="https://staratlas.shop/en-eur/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Star Atlas TV Merch Shop</a></li></ul><p>News &amp; Blogs</p><ul><li><a href="https://thehologram.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">The Hologram</a></li><li><a href="https://medium.com/aephia-industries" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Aephia Medium</a></li><li><a href="https://aephia.com/star-atlas-news/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Aephia News</a></li><li><a href="https://medium.com/@thebountybar" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">The Bounty Bar (ES)</a></li><li><a href="https://www.spacefroggies.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Space Frogies (FR)</a></li></ul><p>UI &amp; Browser Extensions</p><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/Swift42/sagedarkmode" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">SAGE Dark Mode<br></a></li></ul><p>Want to See Your Project Listed?</p><p>Join us on <a href="https://discord.com/invite/staratlas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Discord</a> and contact our moderators</p><br></div></div></main><footer class="VPDocFooter" data-v-39a288b8 data-v-e257564d><!--[--><!--]--><div class="edit-info" data-v-e257564d><!----><div class="last-updated" data-v-e257564d><p class="VPLastUpdated" data-v-e257564d data-v-e98dd255>Last updated: <time datetime="2026-04-16T16:32:35.000Z" data-v-e98dd255></time></p></div></div><nav class="prev-next" aria-labelledby="doc-footer-aria-label" data-v-e257564d><span class="visually-hidden" id="doc-footer-aria-label" data-v-e257564d>Pager</span><div class="pager" data-v-e257564d><a class="VPLink link pager-link prev" href="/introduction/what-is-build" data-v-e257564d><!--[--><span class="desc" data-v-e257564d>Previous</span><span class="title" data-v-e257564d>What is Build?</span><!--]--></a></div><div class="pager" data-v-e257564d><!----></div></nav></footer><!--[--><!--]--></div></div></div><!--[--><!--]--></div></div><footer class="VPFooter has-sidebar" data-v-5d98c3a5 data-v-e31